# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺投資或交易中，為咗避免更大嘅損失而賣出或平倉嘅行為（量詞：次）
eng:cutting losses in investment or trading to avoid greater losses
<eg>
yue:佢見到個市勢唔對路，即刻止蝕。 (keoi5 gin3 dou3 go3 si5 sai3 m4 deoi3 lou6, zik1 hak1 zi2 sit6.)
eng:He immediately cut his losses when he saw the market trend was not right. [end of text]


